In [75], FHE encrypted ECG data are uploaded from a patient to the cloud for detecting LQTC (Long QT Syndrome). Cloud will receive two values, QT and RR. These values are encrypted homomorphically at the patient’s end. Initially, recordings are taken from THEW database [73], and then patient QTc is computed homomorphically as

